<a name="orm-secimi"></a>
## 3. üóÑÔ∏è ORM Se√ßimi: Neden Prisma Deƒüil de Drizzle?

Bu en kritik sorulardan biri. Detaylƒ± a√ßƒ±klayalƒ±m.

### 3.1 Piyasa Durumu

**Prisma:**
- üî• Piyasa payƒ±: ~65-70%
- üë• Kullanƒ±cƒ± sayƒ±sƒ±: 500K+ developers
- üíº Kurumsal kabul: √áok y√ºksek (Vercel, Netlify)
- üìö Ecosystem: Devasa (tooling, plugins)

**Drizzle:**
- üÜï Piyasa payƒ±: ~5-10% (yeni ama hƒ±zla b√ºy√ºyor)
- üë• Kullanƒ±cƒ± sayƒ±sƒ±: 50K+ developers
- üíº Kurumsal kabul: Artan (k√º√ß√ºk-orta ≈üirketler)
- üìö Ecosystem: Geli≈ümekte

### 3.2 Neden Drizzle Se√ßtik?

#### **A. TypeScript-First Design**

**Prisma Schema Language (PSL):**
```prisma
// schema.prisma
model User {
  id        Int      @id @default(autoincrement())
  email     String   @unique
  name      String?
  createdAt DateTime @default(now())
}
```

**Sorunlar:**
- ‚ùå Yeni bir dil √∂ƒürenmeniz gerekir (PSL)
- ‚ùå Code generation gerekir (`prisma generate`)
- ‚ùå Build step ekler
- ‚ùå IDE support sƒ±nƒ±rlƒ±
- ‚ùå Type inference zayƒ±f

**Drizzle:**
```typescript
// sema.ts
export const users = pgTable("users", {
  id: serial("id").primaryKey(),
  email: text("email").notNull().unique(),
  name: text("name"),
  createdAt: timestamp("created_at").defaultNow(),
});

export type User = typeof users.$inferSelect;
export type InsertUser = typeof users.$inferInsert;
```

**Avantajlar:**
- ‚úÖ Saf TypeScript (yeni dil yok)
- ‚úÖ Zero code generation
- ‚úÖ M√ºkemmel IDE support (IntelliSense)
- ‚úÖ Type inference otomatik
- ‚úÖ Compile-time safety

---

#### **B. SQL-Like Query Syntax**

**Prisma:**
```typescript
// Prisma - Kendi API'si
const users = await prisma.user.findMany({
  where: {
